query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_properties,
  COUNT(DISTINCT city) as cities,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM property_images WHERE property_id IN (SELECT id FROM properties WHERE source = 'zillow')) as total_images
FROM properties WHERE source = 'zillow';
